This project enables BOINC to support OpenID on the web server. 

The OpenID features are implemented with the library LightOpenID by mewp (http://gitorious.org/lightopenid). The file
openid.php is the library and its under a MIT license.

The other two files are the modifications required to support OpenID on the BOINC web server.

Installation
============

In order to install/try this version of the web server, you only have to download those three files, plus the button images
for enabling the OpenID feature.

License
=======
All the BOINC files are under GNU Lesser General Public license version 3.


